    {
      "id": "PopularPost260324",
      "post_content": "I like this better than [Wolfir Silverheart](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wolfir Silverheart).  \nDon't get me wrong, Wolfir Silverheart is strong. In fact it's TOO strong, which is why I refrain myself from liking it. I love powerful cards, I just hate it when it is in a pure powercreepy way (pretty much why I also despise [Baneslayer Angel](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Baneslayer Angel)).  \nAs it has been said, this is a 6 power card for 4 mana only. It's good.  \nHell, I'd even go so far as to say that even if Wolfir Silverheart were a 3/3 with Soulbound +3/+3 it would've still been great, as it is it's kind of overwhelming.",
      "posted_by": "Dabok",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost260324\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">I like this better than <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Wolfir Silverheart\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wolfir Silverheart\">Wolfir Silverheart</a>.<br/>Don't get me wrong, Wolfir Silverheart is strong. In fact it's TOO strong, which is why I refrain myself from liking it. I love powerful cards, I just hate it when it is in a pure powercreepy way (pretty much why I also despise <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Baneslayer Angel\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Baneslayer Angel\">Baneslayer Angel</a>).<br/>As it has been said, this is a 6 power card for 4 mana only. It's good.<br/>Hell, I'd even go so far as to say that even if Wolfir Silverheart were a 3/3 with Soulbound +3/+3 it would've still been great, as it is it's kind of overwhelming.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '260324'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy78910\">Dabok</span>\r\n                                (7/31/2012 9:39:13 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: lef